---
import DefaultLayout from '../../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = 'Document Digitization Case Studies: Healthcare, BFSI, Government';
---

<DefaultLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description="Review real-world digitization case studies delivered for hospitals, banks, government departments, and enterprises with measurable retrieval and compliance outcomes."
>
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-700">
        Case Studies
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
        Document digitization success stories.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-sm text-slate-700">
        A few examples of how we have helped customers across healthcare, banking, government and
        enterprises digitize large archives and improve access to records.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">
          Healthcare · 4.5M pages
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Multi‑hospital medical record digitization.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 flex-1 text-xs text-slate-700">
          Legacy MRD archives were scanned and indexed by MRN and specialty, reducing retrieval
          times for medico‑legal and clinical requests.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-emerald-700">
          Result: 70% faster retrieval · Record rooms freed for new use.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-sky-700">
          Banking · 1.2M pages
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
          KYC and loan file digitization for a regional bank.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 flex-1 text-xs text-slate-700">
          Branch‑wise KYC and loan documents were scanned and centralized, with indexing by
          customer ID and account number.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-emerald-700">
          Result: Faster audit response · Reduced carton movement between branches.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-amber-700">
          Government · 800K pages
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Land and citizen record digitization.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 flex-1 text-xs text-slate-700">
          Department archives of land and citizen records were digitized and organized, improving
          turnaround for citizen services and RTI responses.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-emerald-700">
          Result: Better visibility · Less risk of damage to original records.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/10 via-sky-500/10 to-slate-100 p-8 ring-1 ring-emerald-200">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Want to see what this could look like for you?
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          Share your industry, volumes and locations. We can walk you through similar work we have
          delivered and suggest a realistic plan.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="rounded-full bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-md shadow-emerald-500/40 hover:bg-emerald-700"
          >
            Talk to our team
          </a>
          <a
            href="/#cost-calculator"
            class="rounded-full border border-emerald-300 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50"
          >
            Get a free estimate
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>

